
 Purpose:
       FLH invokes the FB file backup utility for each subdirectory
       on the drive specified, starting with the specified path.

       The options supplied on the command line are passed to the FB
       program.

 Format:
               FLH  s:[\path]  [t:]  [options]

 Notes:
       Written for the IBM PC using PC DOS 2.0 or later.
       For public, personal use. By Vernon D. Buerg.

       Version 1, Feb 17, 1989
        - release unused memory from 64k COM segment
        - allow ESCape from console to cancel

